<br>
-Free Peoples<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(245)">Aragorn, King in Exile</a> x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(261)">Legolas, Prince of Mirkwood</a> x3<br>
Lorien Elf x4<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(251)">Elven Bow</a> x4<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(309)">Dwarven Axe</a> x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(180)">Hobbit Sword</a> x2<br>
Ranger Sword x2<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(276)">The White Arrows of Lorien</a> x4<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(63)">Greatest Kingdom of My People</a> x2<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(148)">Still Draws Breath</a> x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(249)">Axe Strike</a> x3<br>
